The Gym Pod

The Gym Pod is Singaporeâ€™s first 24/7, pay-per-use private gym. The Gym Pod also has other offerings such as The Flow Pod, The Grit Pod, The Rumble Pod and The Spin Pod. Gym Pod Experience

Gym Pod Experience is a platform created by the franchise owner of The Gym Pod @ 163 Bukit Merah Central. We are here to improve your experience with our Pod and create a community here in Bukit Merah Central.

Bukit Merah Central has a community of healthy residents and hard-working professionals. The Gym Pod @ 163 Bukit Merah Central provides working professionals an avenue to exercise before and after work, or even during their lunchtime. The private gym helps local residents achieve a healthier lifestyle.
